\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)=P(X=x)=p(1-p)^{x-1},\quad x=1,2,\dots
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Frame
We say that 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 has a 
\series bold
Geometric distribution 
\series default
and we write 
\begin_inset Formula $X\sim{\rm geom}(p)$
\end_inset


\family typewriter
